  <brief_title>Study of the Changes in Metabolic Parameters in Patients Treated With Escitalopram for Six Months</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open-label Study of the Changes in Metabolic Parameters in Patients Treated With Escitalopram for Six Months</official_title>
